The paper deals with decision-making in crowdsourcing systems, which involves multiple agents interacting with each other. This suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) or Social and Information Networks (cs.SI). The paper also discusses trust management, which is a key aspect of cybersecurity (cs.CY). The use of game theory and optimization techniques suggests that the paper could also belong to the sub-categories of Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) or Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC).
